PROJECT.NAME: rTriTgu1-mito
PROJECT.TITLE: Trionyx triunguis, mitochondrial assembly, rTriTgu1-mito.
PROJECT.DESCRIPTION: This project collects the mitochondrial assembly of Trionyx triunguis. The assembly is provided by the European Reference Genome Atlas (ERGA, https://www.erga-biodiversity.eu/) via the Biodiversity Genomics Europe project (BGE, https://biodiversitygenomics.eu/).
